title: 1+ Den w/ private balcony!
posting_body: ['Are you looking for a brand new community to call home?', "Then you're in luck - Lucille would be the perfect fit for you!", 'Managed by Solhem, Lucille is located in the heart of the Northeast Arts District and just minutes from Downtown.', 'Walk your dog along the river, bike throughout the quiet NE streets, and immerse yourself in everything this neighborhood has to offer!', 'Lucille is a sister property to The Julia, located a half-block up Broadway.', 'Lucille features multiple state-of-the-art amenities including a stunning rooftop deck and efficient, upgraded unit interiors for your everyday life.', 'Images of exact unit.', 'Plan V - #519', 'Please note, our online pricing shows the effective monthly rate when factoring in our current specials.', 'However, you would use the special up-front and pay regular market rent $1,950/mo afterwards.', 'This beautiful Plan V is finished with vinyl oak plank flooring and gray quartz countertops.', 'This unit also features a private balcony, prime southeastern sun exposure, and a smart, functional walk-through design.', 'For info on amenities and to apply: <URL>', 'For your Instagram fix: @solhemcompanies', 'Lucille is managed by locally-owned Solhem Companies: <URL>', 'Prices subject to change.', 'Minneapolis -- Mpls -- NE -- Northeast -- U of M -- Boutique -- Luxury -- Scandinavian -- Mid-Century Modern -- Bike Friendly -- Pet, Dog, Cat Friendly -- Green Living -- Sustainable -- Electric Car Charging -- New Construction -- Locally Owned -- Solhem']
